    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Plant trace fossils, microscopic mineral particles secreted by plants which are highly resistant to deterioration. Phytoliths can be a source of important palaeobotanical information.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
